collection.name: alien frens
collection.description:
[**ALIEN FRENS WEBSITE**](https://alienfrens.io) **|** [**ALIEN FRENS TWITTER**](https://TWITTER.COM/ALIENFRENS)

Alien Frens is a community driven collection of 10k randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. Our goal is to build the biggest group of frens in the Metaverse. 1 Alien Fren NFT that provides you not only an awesome PFP and a lifelong frenship with 10k other Frens, but a ticket to our IRL events, Invasions, Exclusive Merch, Comic Books, and more.
